name: GIFSaveOptions

properties.name: colors
properties.description: The number of colors in palette. Not valid for all palette types.

properties.name: ditherAmount
properties.description: The amount of dither. Valid only when 'dither type' is diffusion. Range: 1 to 100.

properties.name: forced
properties.description: The type of colors to force into the color palette.

properties.name: matte
properties.description: The color to use to fill anti-aliased edges adjacent to transparent areas of the image. Default: white.

properties.name: palette
properties.description: The type of palette to use.

properties.name: preserveExactColors
properties.description: If true, protects colors in the image that contain entries in the color table from being dithered. Valid only when 'dither' = diffusion.

properties.name: transparency
properties.description: If true, preserves transparent ares of the image during GIF conversion.

description: Options for saving a document in GIF format.
